Package: sse
Type: Package
Title: Sample Size Estimation
Version: 0.7-17
Author: Thomas Fabbro [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Thomas Fabbro <thomas.fabbro@unibas.ch>
URL: http://r-forge.r-project.org/projects/power/
BugReports: http://r-forge.r-project.org/projects/power/
Description: Provides functions to evaluate user-defined power
        functions for a parameter range, and draws a sensitivity plot.
        It also provides a resampling procedure for semi-parametric
        sample size estimation and methods for adding information to a
        Sweave report.
